{"tid":764854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"阿聯酋擬設房地產網站 到2020年棄用物業中介","createTime":"2018-08-02T09:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T09:56:38.000Z","uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0617eac9e47a2819e7229d0f4d37b19fd6e6d2dd","tid":764854,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:56:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阿聯酋擬設房地產網站 到2020年棄用物業中介</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n迪拜土地部是該國專責土地和房地產事務的政府部門，最近公布計劃，推出一個綜合門戶網站，以處理土地買賣及所有商業和住宅物業租賃等事宜，目標是在2020年前讓所有房地產交易均在網上進行。該網站名為房地產自助交易(Real Estate Self-Transaction，簡稱REST)，旨在消除對物業中介的需求，並便利該國房地產在全球各地進行交易。<br />\n<br />\n該網站已展開開發工作，預計在兩年內投入使用，並將成為迪拜X10倡議的一部分。該倡議是一項政府支持的計劃，旨在「使迪拜領先其他國際城市10年」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾時到香港? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://emerging-markets-research.hktdc.com/business-news/article/%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1/%E9%98%BF%E8%81%AF%E9%85%8B%E6%93%AC%E8%A8%AD%E6%88%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E5%88%B02020%E5%B9%B4%E6%A3%84%E7%94%A8%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%AD%E4%BB%8B/raasean/tc/1/1X4U1FR0/1X0AE4F9.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Femerging-markets-research.hktdc.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Farticle%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%259D%25B1%2F%25E9%2598%25BF%25E8%2581%25AF%25E9%2585%258B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25AB%2599-%25E5%2588%25B02020%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25A3%2584%25E7%2594%25A8%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BB%258B%2Fraasean%2Ftc%2F1%2F1X4U1FR0%2F1X0AE4F9.htm&d=x5BhJw%2Fjm72IKdSWcJudsf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=15ef1cf0\" target=\"_blank\">http://emerging-markets-research.hktdc.com/business-news/article/%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1/%E9%98%BF%E8%81%AF%E9%85%8B%E6%93%AC%E8%A8%AD%E6%88%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E5%88%B02020%E5%B9%B4%E6%A3%84%E7%94%A8%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%AD%E4%BB%8B/raasean/tc/1/1X4U1FR0/1X0AE4F9.htm</a>"}]}